Tests should be in __tests__ folder at the same place that the file. 

ex: [SQLiteBiologicalAnalysisRepository.ts](mdc:src/adapters/repositories/SQLiteBiologicalAnalysisRepository.ts) and [SQLiteBiologicalAnalysisRepository.spec.ts](mdc:src/adapters/repositories/__tests__/SQLiteBiologicalAnalysisRepository.spec.ts)


Every adapters should have an in memory instance to test usecases
ex: 
src/adapters/repositories/SQLiteBiologicalAnalysisRepository.ts
src/adapters/repositories/InMemoryBiologicalAnalysisRepository.ts

In memroy will be use to test usecases